subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Shabazz Napier scored 25 points to lead the seventh-seeded Huskies past the fourth-seeded Spartans and into to the Final Four, where they will face top-seeded Florida.
